@node _bug "Known Bugs and Incompatibilities"
@font helvetica.font 11


@{b}Visual Prefs@{ub}
Depth Gadget of the boards window is not working.

->Solution:
Visual Prefs is a hack that causes sometimes problems. You have to edit
the VPrefs settings to get PairsNG started; under VPrefs you have to click
right from the windows depth gadget to select ?!! This is not a bug of
PairsNG.


@{b}Problems with the stone selection@{ub}
If it occurs that the pairs won't build up after they are clicked right, you
could try to change the double click delay in Prefs/Input, e.g. change it to 2.04s


@{b}Slow Gameplay@{ub}

->Solution: 
It is recommended to close all background windows on your Workbench, you doesn't need.

Turn off the highlighting mode (press F4 in-game, or pre-select in the Main Menu -> Marker off)

@endnode


@node "_hardware" "System requirements"
@font helvetica.font 11

@{b}Hardware requirements for PairsNG:@{ub}

- 8 MB Fast-RAM free
- Graphicsboard running CybergraphX V3  or Picasso96 software - min. 15-Bit
- accelerationboard with own RAM recommended (68030 for minimum)
- Amiga OS3.0 (only tested under OS 3.5)
- AHI for Sound

@{b}Screenmodes:@{ub}
- minimum 640*480 (only beginner-mode playable)
- 800*600 - beginner+normal modes playable
- screenmode of 1024*768 RECOMMENDED - all modes playable

@{b}tested with:@{ub}
 Amiga 4000D - Cybervision3D, CGFX V3, 68040/40 (CSMKII), OS 3.5
 Amiga 4000T - CybervisonPPC, PPC/68060, CGFX V3, OS3.5
 Amiga 4000D - Picasso IV, 68060, Picasso96, OS 3.9
 Amiga 4000T - PPC mit MorphOS 0.4ß
 Pegasos-I - PPC750cxe, 600 Mhz, MorphOS 1.4
 WinUAE


@{b}Untested:@{ub}
Amithlon, AmigaXL, Amiga models with Workbench OS3.0 or OS3.1.




@endnode


@node _faq "The PairsNG FAQ - Frequently asked questions"
@font helvetica.font 11

@{b}Frequently asked questions:@{ub}


@{b}Is there a PPC-version in development ?@{ub}
A PPC-version is not planed. But PairsNG uses indirectly the PPC,
if you have installed a PPC JPEG/JFIF datatype (WOS or PPC).

@{b}While playing the game stopped with a debug requester.@{ub} 
The current version is still Beta with activated debug mode! If the 
engine has noticed a bug - the game will be aborted and a window will be
openend, displaying a number; eg. f1b2. If this occures, please send this
code to me. The error will be removed immediatly. Please check my homepage
for updates. It's important to send me a debugcode if one should occure; so
thank you very much.

@{b}The graphic of the skin/stones looks abnormal, what's wrong ?@{ub}
Your JPEG/JFIF datatype is unusable or too old. Please install a new version.

@{b}Will future versions of PairsNG support PAL/NTSC resolutions under OCS/ECS/AGA ?@{ub}
Definitly not. Please upgrade your Amiga with a graphics board.




@endnode

@node _install "Install"
@font helvetica.font 11

@{b}Installation@{ub}
To install PairsNG, simply drag the folder-icon to the desired destination on your 
hard disk. That's all!

PairsNG is designed, to work without any assigns or installations in several 
system folders. If you want, you can copy the fonts&libs to your system folder.



@endnode

